## Mandatory UI workflow

For every UI, UX, frontend styling, component, layout, dashboard, responsive, accessibility, form, table, navigation, animation, or visual-review task, use `/perfect-ui-skill`. Follow the existing project design system before generic defaults. Require semantic tokens, complete component states, responsive behavior, WCAG 2.2 AA checks, reduced motion, loading/error/empty states, and rendered verification before declaring completion.
